      <title>King Street 的信贷对冲基金失去了一位顶级投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/king-street-loses-one-of-its-top-investors-at-credit-hedge-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保罗·戈德施密德 (Paul Goldschmid) 是 King Street Capital Management 任职时间最长的合伙人之一，他将离开这家资产规模 260 亿美元的对冲基金公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/king-street-loses-one-of-its-top-investors-at-credit-hedge-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 16:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金钱卧底：Sarah Samuels，NEPC 加入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/money-undercover-sarah-samuels-nep-seeds-joins-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为机构提供咨询的 NEPC 合伙人 Sarah Samuels 强调了当今私人市场面临的挑战和机遇。她强调，仅靠公开市场无法实现机构回报目标，而 CIO 思维对于驾驭当前形势至关重要。她与 Lisa Abramowicz 在“彭博市场”节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/money-undercover-sarah-samuels-nep-seeds-joins-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 21:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
